{
  "stem": "8784.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Of course, the, the people that they took out of the ghetto were full of fear.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They had no idea where they were being taken.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But as it happens, they took the 100 of us to a back yard of a factory in the city of Cracow.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "In other words, they crossed the, crossed into the city of Cracow itself, and they dropped us off in the back yard of a factory.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We had no idea what this factory is, who, who runs this factory.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We had absolutely no idea why we are there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We had an idea maybe we'll go to work by then.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But when we came there, the SS guards quickly kicked us into formation.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And as we stood in an orderly assembly, the SS guards shouted out to a civilian that was there to inspect the people they brought in for work.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "As it turns out to be this civilian was Oskar Schindler.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And in 1942 when he came over to inspect us, he was looking to receive 100 people that would be strong workers.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "When he took a look at this group of 100 people, he has selected two people out of this group and one of them myself.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And he yelled out to the SS guards in German, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "What that means is that I don't need any children here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We have to make some allowances to Schindler for that time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "This is 1942--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was sometime the end of summer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in, in 1942, Schindler was neither an important person that the SS guards would recognize.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Schindler potentially was looking for strong workers at the same time.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
